<L>__{interior hotel lobby. day}
<A>__{paul works his way through the crowds in the lobby, sees a trolley of dishes by an elevator, looks around, can't see any staff. disgusted, he pushes the trolley himself.}
<L>__{interior hotel kitchen. day}
<A>__{paul pushes the trolley into the deserted kitchen. at the back door, several cooks listen to the radio.}
<C>__{radio announcer}
<D>__{'good hutus, we must destroy an infestation of cockroaches at the technical college.'}
<C>__{paul}
<D>__{turn that off. we have a hotel to run.}
<A>__{the cooks halfheartedly slouch back to the sinks.}
